title: Trash of A Dark Fantasy
description: Trash of A Dark Fantasy Manhwa I got transmigrated to a dark fantasy MMORPG and became the ruined character I raised, 다크 판타지의 망캐가 되었다, Doomed Character Of A Dark Fantasy World Synopsis : Not impossible, but rejected…? I didn’t even give myself time to think, I opened my eyes in the middle of a swamp. As a trash character, I leveled. A brutal and ominous world. Filled with those who worship chaos and abyss, rushing towards the brink of destruction in a dark age. This is the story of a survival journey in the dark fantasy, the survival of a trash character.
